title: Episode 1: Rachel Wharton & Keith Wagstaff
description: Rachel Wharton of Edible Brooklyn/Manhattan & Keith Wagstaff of City Search join Cathy to talk about morning after breakfast, good egg cooking techniques, and the vegetarian/meat eater clash on the debut episode of “Cheap Date”.
